Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveReport from Abia state indicates that gunmen have kidnapped the Prelate of the Methodist Church Nigeria, His Eminence, Samuel Kanu.
It was gathered that he was kidnapped alongside two other senior priests of the Church on Sunday afternoon.
It was further gathered that the trio were abducted along Enugu/Port-harcourt expressway on their way from a church programme.
Already, Police authorities have confirmed the development with assurance of making efforts to rescue them.

